Entities.script: (function(){ var yes = {}; var no = {};     function change(entityID) {     yes = Overlays.addOverlay("text", {     x: 242,     y: 370,     width: 64,     height: 64,     backgroundColor: { red: 0, green: 0, blue: 0},     color: { red: 255, green: 255, blue: 0},     font: {size: 25},     topMargin: 8,     name: "adrian",     visible: true,     text: " Yes" });      }     this.enterEntity = function(entityID) {         print("enterEntity("+entityID+")");         print(GlobalServices.username);         change(entityID);     };     this.leaveEntity = function(entityID) {         print("leaveEntity("+entityID+")");         Entities.editEntity(entityID, { angularDamping: 0.5});         Entities.editEntity(entityID, { color: { red: 255, green: 190, blue: 20} });        var life = Overlays.getOverlayAtPoint({x:242,y:370});                  print(JSON.stringify(life));           print(JSON.stringify(yes));                Overlays.deleteOverlay(yes);     }; })
